{"type": "article", "id": 43305, "title": "这把藤椅有点萌，绝不是你爸用过的那种｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-23T23:17:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42606, "name": "Ancla Studio"}, {"id": 42592, "name": "Afternoon Tea"}, {"id": 42607, "name": "Brickmonkey"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170724071718SIkRJjtmnafDbxCQ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Sila</h3><p>法国腕表品牌 <a href=\"http://www.sila-paris.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sila</a> 起源于联合创始人 Alexandra Peltre Marque 对于现有女士腕表款式的不满，在她眼中，它们大多只是在男款上稍作修改，缺少创意和女性化的感觉。当 Peltre Marque 在东京一家商店内，发现了一枚娇小、像是珠宝一样的复古腕表后，受到了启发，最终带领团队设计了强调小巧、简约以及将可替换表带作为主打特色的 Sila。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1059084180/sila-the-feminine-watch-revolution\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 99 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210904jWbzo6ZwQOnRAFSf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210904IZv5GDJeHb8sLpBO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707232109032AjVFgY6wWfZxt9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.445588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210903U3BcJ0AHMGRlpVo5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Swimming robot by PipeGuard</h3><p>据麻省理工学院的统计，城市中有 20% 的水因为水管泄漏而浪费，然而现有的泄漏检测技术不仅昂贵、耗时，还会受管道材料的限制无法通用。为此，校内一支名为 Pipe Guard 的团队历时九年时间，研发了一个形状类似羽毛球的小型机器人，让它负责检测水管泄漏。沿着水管漂流的过程中，机器人下半部分与管壁触碰的“裙摆”探测器会记录受力变化，从而推断出是哪个部分出现了泄漏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210849zD9NoUtywEJeHPAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210849nXtRNwvWubBU168M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667254\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Alice’s Curious Garden by Afternoon Tea &amp; Disney</h3><p>来一场《爱丽丝梦游仙境》中的茶话会会是什么模样？最近，围绕下午茶文化的日本复合概念品牌 <a href=\"https://www.afternoon-tea.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Afternoon Tea</a> 与迪士尼合作推出了以这一经典童话为主题的<a href=\"https://www.afternoon-tea.net/article/seasonal-item/alice2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">联名企划</a>，并且根据“现实”与“幻想”两种世界观设计相应的产品。除了化妆包、手机架以及文具类用品之外，还有专为小朋友设计的围兜和配套的亲子围裙。你可以通过<a href=\"http://shop.afternoon-tea.net/shop/e/efeature-alice/?utm_source=brandsite&amp;utm_medium=brandsite&amp;utm_campaign=alice2017_seasonal-item_3\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些商品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210835iOfCwtvznpj3LkRS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210835Ca5Dpzr4vtcEwMZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210836c6oNeyrjqHZghFDl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210835q20dZARuYkXClmtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210837NGownSFuxiQPb4Ov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Gandia by Andrea Mestre</h3><p>厌倦了刻板冰冷的办公椅，英国皇家艺术学院的毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.andreamestre.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrea Mestre</a> 带来了一把鼓励人们在办公间隙活动的藤椅 Gandia。他利用藤条本身的可塑性，打造出充满圆拱的结构，椅背和两侧一体化的扶手通过能够自由活动的关节相连，因此可以自由调整座位的角度和位置。相比起常见于办公椅的塑料，选用生长周期更快的藤条也体现了对环保的重视。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210822QGm5tN2eTuCPDlAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210822ZFHLi28x7MREoWKk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.601523\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210822yFt2i4kpZnmVlrAa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Elbphilharmonie by Brickmonkey</h3><p>来自德国汉堡的 <a href=\"https://brickmonkey.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brickmonkey</a> 是一间擅长搭建和设计创意乐高模型的公司，他们之前的作品包括蒸汽朋克风格的飞船以及真实世界的建筑模型。为了庆祝汉堡新地标易北爱乐厅（Elbphilharmonie Hamburg Concert Hall）开幕，团队耗时 110 个小时，用两万块积木创作了一款还原度相当高的模型。他们利用圆形积木再现了波浪形的屋顶，打开正中央的部分后，还能近距离欣赏音乐厅的细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707232109579Ub1KQxkSrYqlctW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210957u9sjBMlE2ROcygGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017072321095723xX14teAKrcuIWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707232109577RueXzPxoE5J2FwL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Hip Water by Ancla Studio</h3><p>墨西哥创意工作室 <a href=\"http://anclastudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ancla</a> 最近为当地的一款水果风味水品牌设计了品牌形象。标签上的几何图形都是根据水果的造型和颜色得来的，中间的品牌名 Hip 采用了镂空设计，强调产品本身新鲜清爽的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210806qoD2HfZEn0Tw9mRe.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.450000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210806YVswLKi3qlEPIJcB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.885333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170723210806WhaubgENI92rZOlY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.450000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}